metadata.description:
Sinematic is an EP produced by the NFT Jingles Creative Roster, being released on all streaming platforms and as an NFT. This group of individuals under the guidance of NFT Jingles has been tasked with breaking the boundary between web2 and web3 music. 

Enjoy your Sinematic experience - Here to entertain and giveback 

* Tracks: 

Track 1 - Hato(Feat. Cloudy The Weatherman & Rooks), 

Track 2 - Love & Sin(Feat. Dieverse24k & Cloudy The Weatherman), 

Track 3 - Prototype(Feat. Tek47 & Cloudy The Weatherman), 

Track 4 - What's The Operation(Feat. Cloudy The Weatherman & Lucky), 

Track 5 - Sinematic(Feat. Cloudy The Weatherman)
metadata.name: NFT Jingles - Sinematic
